"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-07-28-Medal-events-to-watch-at-2024-Paris-Summer-Olympics-on-July-28-1vBFqF0FyRa-p.html\", \"text\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use. You can change your cookie settings through your browser.  Sports Scene  Copied  A total of 13 gold medals will be decided on July 28 at the 2024 Paris Summer Olympics. CGTN Sports Scene recommends the following competitions:  First, the women's skateboarding street final will take place at the Place de la Concord at 17:00 (GMT+2).  Less than a quarter-hour later, the women's archery team final will be contested at Les Invalides at 17:11 (CMT+2).  Then at 20:30 (GMT+2), two of the most eye-catching swimming events of the day \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 the men's 400-meter individual medley final and women's 100-meter butterfly final \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 will get underway at the Olympic Aquatics Centre in the Paris La Defense Arena.  And at 22:15 (GMT+2) at the Grand Palais, the best-performing fencer will win the men's epee individual gold medal.  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\"}"